    "The agent's output is the action (control signal of the system).",
    "The parameters of the RL algorithm are the sample rate is 4s, the discount factor is 0.99 and the learning rate is 0.005.",
    "Table 4 DQNL agent parameters Parameter Value The frequency at which the agent receives feedback from the environment is known as the sample rate, while the extent to which the agent updates its internal model based on the newly received information is determined by the learning rate.",
